Package: SparkRext
Type: Package
Title: SparkR extension for dplyr
Description: This package reimplement data wrangling functions to override dplyr generics instead.
This allows users to use same sets of functions for both Spark DataFrame and R DataFrame in the same session.
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2015-10-28
